t to fire protection engineering students, like Nasim, and the invaluable awards it sponsors to Canadian Colleges, like Seneca Polytechnic, remains unwavering.<\/p>\n<p>As we move forward, we are eager to continue our fruitful collaboration, empowering aspiring fire protection professionals and supporting their educational journey.<\/p>\n<h3>A Fire Protection Engineering Career at Viking<\/h3>\n<p>For the last 90 years, Viking has strived to protect lives and property. Our company\u2019s solid reputation is built on our commitment to provide top-of-the-line fire protection products and services that specifically meet our clients demands.<\/p>\n<p>Along with the global vision and spirit of innovation that we all share, we expect all of our employees to work in teams and build relationships based on trust and equity. Doing so allows us to provide quality customer service based on honesty, integrity, and transparency. Our team\u2019s values reflect our management philosophy, and we count on each employee\u2019s motivation and dedication to fulfill our mission.<\/p>\n<p>Come learn and develop your fire protection engineering job experience with the best in the fire protection industry. At Viking you will find a work environment that will support your professional growth, so that you can become the expert of tomorrow.<\/p>\n<p>Our staffing process, takes into account our company\u2019s mission and strategic objectives, is free of discrimination, and promotes job equity. Viking Fire Protection is always on the lookout for the most qualified candidates whose trade skills and experience match our <a href=\"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/job\/\">job posting<\/a>\u00a0requirements.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/join-the-team\/\">Apply today<\/a>\u00a0and join one of Canada\u2019s most respected fire protection companies!<\/p>\n<p>For future engineering students considering the noble pursuit of saving lives and safeguarding property, Viking Fire Protection offers an extraordinary and fulfilling career path. Prepare to be astounded by the countless possibilities working as a fire protection engineer holds. By joining forces with Viking, you can fuel your passion for fire safety, develop essential skills, and open doors to a dynamic and rewarding career.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Shining Stars: Nasim Boroomand and Zoey Mcqueen are the Winners of Our Seneca Polytechnic Engineering Students Awards! Each year, Seneca College takes great pride in recognizing the outstanding achievements of its students and acknowledging the remarkable support from donors and advocates at the annual Seneca Awards. At the 2024 Seneca Polytechnic Awards ceremony, the exceptional [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":8739,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[43],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1538","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-employee-stories","cf"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1538","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1538"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1538\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":8801,"href":"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1538\/revisions\/8801"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/8739"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-js